phrases: My friend wants to meet behind the school building.
The kind lady who has shown affection to as gross a man as Yamane-dono.
Why would you bring me here when you are alone together?
It is the first time a girl's asked me to meet behind the school.
I was afraid of coming alone, so I wanted you to come along.
S-So what did you want, Kurihara-san?
I made too much pudding, so I thought I would share it.
Yamane-dono appears to be so fixed on his ugliness,
he cannot understand what the lady is trying to do.
Accept it with the greatest of gratefulness.
She made it with you in mind.
If Yamane is not going to budge...
I shall leave you two alone
You are accepting the pudding, Yamane-dono!
I do not think I should be the only one, though...
She made that pudding for you, Yamane-dono!
Kuriyama-san's sharing them out of courtesy!
She called you behind the school.
It is not out of courtesy!
You have noticed, have you not?
About how Kurihara-dono feels about you?
Rumors would start flying if she gave me pudding in public!
You are far too self-deprecating, Yamane-dono.
I did not push you that hard.
It seems that Kurihara-dono is more important to you
Then I shall be on my way.
W-Would you please take a hint?
I am embarrassed with my terrible acting.
I want to get out of here!
Next time, I will make some for you, too, okay?
She is a better woman than I would imagined.
I think my girlfriend's been on edge lately.
Goda-kun, could you open this lid for me?
Kamine, have I done something recently?
I get the sense that you are angry at me.
I am pretty sure Kamine's angry about something.
I need to apologize to Kamine.
I need to go to our usual meeting spot.
Did you think I went home?
I thought you were done with me.
I wanted you to worry about me, so I was being a bit mean.
You were so angry at me that you had to be mean?
Are not you going to hold hands with me?
I mean, you held hands with Patricia-chan.
Are you upset that I arm wrestled with Patricia?
I would have arm wrestled with you.
It is not that I want to arm wrestle with you.
In fact, I do not want you to.
Nah, you will just hate me if I told you.
Why would I ever hate you, Kamine?
I am your boyfriend, are not I?
I will hear anything you need to say.
Do not get too close to other girls.
Call me by my first name from now on.
I cannot blame Patricia-chan, but I am the only one who can call you Takeru.
And do not hold hands with other girls,
I am the only one who can hold hands with you.
You can help them open plastic bottles,
but if you are nice to someone, you have to be even nicer to me!
So that is what it was.
I am so needy, are not I?
No, but you did surprise me.
I know I am being stupid, too!
It is been a while since my girlfriend and I started dating,
but we have not even kissed yet.
How can I get to kiss her?
Is not that Goda and Kamine-san?
They do not mess around in class.
They have been doing it here.
Are not you going to call me by my first name?
I just wanted you to say my name.
I will say your name as much as you want, Ayaka.
I guess people do change when they are in love.
Kami Ayaka, you have changed since we started going out.
You have gotten cuter, too, Kana-san.
Can I be more needy, then?
D-Does it really work like that?
How much is Goda kissing all the time?
It is that sense of initiative that you do not have, Chiaki!
Wait, Goda-kun, I was not ready for that!
Takeru-kun, you are always so sudden.
You expect me to do that?!
There is nothing wrong with the girl making the first move.
Jeez, and you call yourself a guy?
Let us do it properly next time.
Okay, I will kiss you, then.
On the count of three, then?
Hey, it is Chiaki-kun and Kana-san.
What are you guys doing here?
I am going to kiss my girlfriend today!
E-Everyone is on vacation right now.
Oh, what time do you have to be home today?
No, I will take it even further.
I have to be home by eight.
I mean, we have not even kissed yet,
so I kind of expected that much, but...
Am I wearing good undies today?
Why do not we study for exams?
Is the air conditioner setting okay?
I-I guess it is a bit hot.
I decided I would make a move today!
I will get something to drink.
I am going to strike out again.
Why cannot I just go for it?
We are running out of time.
I have to leave before seven.
I want the mood to be right for our first kiss, though.
There is no point rushing it.
And why are you so red?
I do not want to do it like this!
You keep telling me to take the initiative!
That does not mean anything goes!
Besides, our first kiss is going to be a precious memory.
I do want to kiss you, too, but I want to kiss the normal Chiaki.
I do not need a special mood or anything.
I just want to kiss you normally.
I cannot believe you would rely on that stuff.
Next time, why not start one pretending that you are getting attacked by an alien?
Or how about a soccer PK goal into one?
That was just another one of our skits.
I am done with our duo!
How am I supposed to react to that?
